comments: Nurkic (POR) immediately slides his hand off of Jokic's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Simons (POR) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Murray (DEN) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) has his arm slightly out of the frame of his body and marginal contact occurs to Grant's (POR) body as Jokic releases away during his roll to the basket.
Nurkic (POR) places his hand to Jokic's (DEN) side and marginal body contact occurs defending Jokic's (DEN) post move.
Nurkic (POR) cleanly blocks Jokic's (DEN) shot attempt at the basket.
Gordon (DEN) and Hart (POR) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Hart (POR) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself with his arm slightly extended and marginal contact occurs to Grant's (POR) side as he defends over the pick.
Nurkic (POR) brings his arm toward Murray's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs during Murray's (DEN) drive.
Hart (POR) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Lillard (POR) is moving alongside Murray's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Murray's (DEN) drive.
Nurkic (POR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Brown (DEN) places his forearm to Simons' (POR) side defending his drive and removes it, without applying force at the start of his upward shooting motion.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Grant's (POR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Brown (DEN) establishes himself in Nurkic's (POR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Nurkic (POR) places his forearm to Jokic's (DEN) back and marginal lower body contact occurs during his drive.
Jokic (DEN) brings his off-arm toward Nurkic's (POR) side and marginal contact occurs as Jokic (DEN) attempts to dribble around Nurkic (POR).
Jokic (DEN) brings both hands to the ball as he gathers and marginal contact occurs with Nurkic (POR) as Nurkic (POR) is retreating his arm away.
Gordon (DEN) elevates and brushes Hart's (POR) shoulder as they pursue the loose ball.
Lillard (POR) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Gordon's (DEN) arm after the release.
Nurkic (POR) turns to roll and marginal contact occurs with Murray (DEN) as Murray (DEN) goes under the pick.
Murray (DEN) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Brown (DEN) establishes himself in Nurkic's (POR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Nurkic (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it away from Jokic (DEN) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Grant (POR) closes out towards Murray's (DEN) side contesting his jump shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs after his release.
Grant (POR) already in Brown's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as they both roll toward the basket.
Nurkic (POR) is absorbing the initial contact that occurs with Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and incidental contact occurs as Caldwell-Pope (DEN) attempts to move over the screen.
